<h1>Media Kit</h1>

<p>Pre-approved media for promoting DJ Sprenk. Please <a href="/contact">contact</a> before any modifications or using alternative media.</p>

<h2>Bio</h2>
<p>
  DJ Sprenk is a DJ based out of Cambridge, MA, USA, specializing in Brazilian Zouk. He's known for his dynamic, moving,
  and musical sets that challenge convention and connect deeply with dancers across the world.
</p>

